Union MaybeI32 has none; some value: i32.

To consume cells cells: owned buffer of i32, giving i32.
Give length of cells.

To guarded move maybe: MaybeI32, giving i32.
Let cells be owned buffer of 4 i32 filled with 1.
Let result be 0.
Match maybe:
MaybeI32.some with value when value is greater than zero: result becomes consume cells move cells;
MaybeI32.some with value: result becomes consume cells move cells;
MaybeI32.none: result becomes consume cells move cells.
Give result.

To main, giving i32.
Give guarded move MaybeI32.some with value be 7.
